873
00:59:18,284 --> 00:59:21,036
-[So-yeon whimpers]
-[Man-bae] Drop the gun. I'm serious.

874
00:59:21,120 --> 00:59:22,788
-Drop the gun, asshole!
-Drop the knife.

875
00:59:23,664 --> 00:59:26,584
I'm gonna kill her. I said drop the gun!

876
00:59:27,293 --> 00:59:28,711
Final warning. Got it?

877
00:59:29,795 --> 00:59:30,713
Drop the knife.

878
00:59:30,796 --> 00:59:32,965
[Man-bae] I'm giving you my final warning.

879
00:59:34,133 --> 00:59:36,552
-[gun clicks]
-I'm really gonna kill her.

880
00:59:36,635 --> 00:59:39,138
You hear? Drop the gun now.

881
00:59:40,139 --> 00:59:41,515
Drop the fucking gun!

882
00:59:41,599 --> 00:59:44,476
I will slash this lady if you don't!
Drop the gun!

883
00:59:44,560 --> 00:59:48,981
-[Man-bae yelps]
-[So-yeon whimpering]

884
00:59:51,275 --> 00:59:52,484
Did you get hurt anywhere?

885
00:59:53,193 --> 00:59:54,778
[breathes deeply]

886
