926
01:02:07,745 --> 01:02:09,538
[man 2] Everyone freeze!

927
01:02:10,539 --> 01:02:14,460
[poignant music playing]

928
01:02:18,297 --> 01:02:19,548
I've got Ms. Yoon.

929
01:02:20,048 --> 01:02:22,634
She's safe. It's thanks to you. Great job.

930
01:02:23,594 --> 01:02:24,928
Thanks very much.

931
01:02:27,723 --> 01:02:29,057
Thanks for everything.

932
01:02:33,729 --> 01:02:34,730
[sighs]

933
01:02:36,273 --> 01:02:37,441
[exhales]

934
01:02:38,650 --> 01:02:41,570
-[man 3] All right. This way.
-[man 4] Straight ahead.

935
01:02:42,362 --> 01:02:43,489
[music fades]

936
01:02:48,160 --> 01:02:49,077
Oh, Mom!

937
01:02:50,704 --> 01:02:51,705
[gasps]

938
01:02:53,791 --> 01:02:57,336
-[Woo-jin] Mom!
-[cries happily]

939
01:02:57,419 --> 01:02:58,504
[So-yeon exhales]

940
01:03:01,590 --> 01:03:02,925
[Woo-jin] You're okay.

941
01:03:03,884 --> 01:03:06,970
I'm so sorry. I'm so, so sorry.

942
01:03:07,054 --> 01:03:08,263
[Woo-jin cries]

943
01:03:09,264 --> 01:03:10,808
It took me so long.

944
01:03:11,475 --> 01:03:13,852
-I'll do better.
-It's okay. It's all right.

945
01:03:14,895 --> 01:03:15,938
It's okay.

946
01:03:16,438 --> 01:03:17,606
[So-yeon cries]

947
01:03:23,195 --> 01:03:25,197
[Woo-jin cries]

948
01:03:25,989 --> 01:03:28,200
-[Woo-jin] I'm so sorry, Mom.
-[exhales]

949
01:03:31,453 --> 01:03:33,455
[sirens wailing]

950
01:03:33,539 --> 01:03:35,541
[suspenseful music playing]

951
01:03:44,174 --> 01:03:45,467
-[loud pop]
-[tires squealing]

952
01:03:45,551 --> 01:03:47,719
What happened? Uh… Oh! [gasps]

953
01:03:48,262 --> 01:03:49,179
[tires screech]

954
01:03:58,105 --> 01:04:00,148
[device whirs, booms]

955
01:04:00,232 --> 01:04:01,275
[loud click]

956
01:04:12,828 --> 01:04:14,288
-[gas hissing]
-[sputtering]

957
01:04:36,852 --> 01:04:38,103
[cell phone buzzes]

958
01:04:40,147 --> 01:04:42,024
CHOI SIN-HYEONG

959
01:04:45,152 --> 01:04:45,986
KANG TAE-YEONG

960
01:04:46,069 --> 01:04:48,322
SIR, I ROUTED 860 BITCOIN
TO YOUR WALLET

961
01:04:55,579 --> 01:04:56,705
[music fades]

962
01:05:05,255 --> 01:05:06,465
[Gun-woo] Mom.

963
01:05:07,507 --> 01:05:09,718
No, Mom! Woo-jin!

964
01:05:09,801 --> 01:05:11,929
[Gun-woo breathing heavily]

965
01:05:12,554 --> 01:05:14,181
No, Mom! [yells]

966
01:05:14,806 --> 01:05:17,643
[breathes heavily]

967
01:05:18,143 --> 01:05:19,645
-[Gun-woo exhales]
-You okay?

968
01:05:21,146 --> 01:05:22,064
[Gun-woo sighs]

969
01:05:23,857 --> 01:05:24,691
[sighs]

970
01:05:26,151 --> 01:05:27,402
Do you need some water?

971
01:05:31,865 --> 01:05:32,824
Woo-jin,

972
01:05:34,076 --> 01:05:35,702
I'm hungry after that nightmare.

973
01:05:37,704 --> 01:05:40,749
Let's go. I'll make ramyeon for you.

974
01:05:42,626 --> 01:05:43,460
Deal.

975
01:05:48,715 --> 01:05:50,717
[footsteps approach]

976
01:05:52,594 --> 01:05:53,428
[gasps]

977
01:06:05,524 --> 01:06:06,441
Oh.

978
01:06:18,829 --> 01:06:19,997
[Woo-jin] Oh!

979
01:06:20,664 --> 01:06:21,748
-Let's eat.
-[Gun-woo] Yes.

980
01:06:22,249 --> 01:06:24,376
[gentle music playing]

981
01:06:46,064 --> 01:06:47,024
[sighs]

982
01:06:50,777 --> 01:06:51,903
-Woo-jin.
-Hmm?

983
01:06:54,031 --> 01:06:55,073
Let's find another house.

984
01:06:57,409 --> 01:07:01,371
I still feel anxious.
Like Im Baek-jeong's planning to return.

985
01:07:05,333 --> 01:07:06,168
Let's go then.

986
01:07:08,003 --> 01:07:09,421
And also,

987
01:07:10,297 --> 01:07:12,257
we'll train for more battles to come.

988
01:07:12,758 --> 01:07:14,009
We'll be ready for the next one.

989
01:07:14,885 --> 01:07:15,886
What battles?

990
01:07:16,636 --> 01:07:18,346
We'll train to fight the bloodhounds.

991
01:07:21,391 --> 01:07:23,310
[quiet suspenseful music playing]

992
01:07:23,393 --> 01:07:26,480
Then next time,
I promise I won't back down at all.

993
01:07:27,147 --> 01:07:28,565
I'll also get stronger.

994
01:07:29,733 --> 01:07:31,151
We will never lose.

995
01:07:36,073 --> 01:07:37,866
-Ack.
-Ack.

996
01:07:37,949 --> 01:07:39,951
[music builds]

997
01:07:42,120 --> 01:07:43,121
Let's finish it.

998
01:07:54,341 --> 01:07:55,425
[music fades]

999
01:08:02,766 --> 01:08:03,892
[moans]

1000
01:08:06,311 --> 01:08:07,729
[tense music playing]

1001
01:08:08,772 --> 01:08:10,023
[Baek-jeong exhales]

1002
01:08:18,365 --> 01:08:20,617
This is our first meeting,
so we'll get to the point.

1003
01:08:21,660 --> 01:08:25,497
The person who is your contact
that helped you with the IKFC in Bangkok,

1004
01:08:25,997 --> 01:08:26,915
tell me his name.

1005
01:08:49,146 --> 01:08:50,814
I can kill you right now.

1006
01:08:53,233 --> 01:08:55,485
Ten, nine,

1007
01:08:56,194 --> 01:08:57,070
eight,

1008
01:08:57,654 --> 01:08:58,697
seven,

1009
01:08:58,780 --> 01:08:59,865
six,

1010
01:08:59,948 --> 01:09:01,241
five,

1011
01:09:01,324 --> 01:09:02,367
four,

1012
01:09:03,076 --> 01:09:04,077
three--

1013
01:09:04,161 --> 01:09:05,036
All right.

1014
01:09:07,164 --> 01:09:08,540
[sighs]

1015
01:09:08,623 --> 01:09:09,457
Name.

1016
01:09:10,500 --> 01:09:11,668
Paichit Chaichana.

1017
01:09:14,421 --> 01:09:15,505
I've heard on the street

1018
01:09:15,589 --> 01:09:18,758
that bastard's bringing in one ton of meth
into Korea this fall.

1019
01:09:19,342 --> 01:09:21,219
It's worth about 300 billion won.

1020
01:09:22,179 --> 01:09:23,013
Yeah, so?

1021
01:09:23,096 --> 01:09:24,723
You scratch my back

1022
01:09:25,223 --> 01:09:26,808
and I'll scratch yours.

1023
01:09:31,271 --> 01:09:33,982
We're all someone else's bloodhounds.

1024
01:09:34,482 --> 01:09:36,193
Don't be upset about that.

1025
01:09:38,528 --> 01:09:39,905
Will you be a bloodhound?

1026
01:09:40,780 --> 01:09:42,616
-[gun clicks]
-Huh.

1027
01:09:48,371 --> 01:09:49,414
[grunts] Hmm.

1028
01:09:49,998 --> 01:09:51,082
[chuckles softly]

1029
01:09:52,751 --> 01:09:53,585
Ae-seo.

1030
01:09:53,668 --> 01:09:55,670
[suspenseful music playing]

1031
01:10:04,512 --> 01:10:05,764
I'll make it look nice.

1032
01:10:14,898 --> 01:10:16,024
[music fades]

1033
01:10:19,277 --> 01:10:21,279
[tense electronic music playing]

1034
01:13:10,907 --> 01:13:12,033
[music fades]

1035
01:13:29,134 --> 01:13:31,136
[somber music playing]

1036
01:13:39,185 --> 01:13:40,103
[music fades]
